    "Mori requires tmux to manage terminal sessions. Please install tmux and relaunch the app.\n\nInstall via Homebrew:\n  brew install tmux\n\nOr via MacPorts:\n  sudo port install tmux": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mori 需要 tmux 来管理终端会话。请安装 tmux 后重新启动应用。\n\n通过 Homebrew 安装：\n  brew install tmux\n\n或通过 MacPorts 安装：\n  sudo port install tmux"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "OK": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "好"
